Package: libanyevent-onkyo-perl
Architecture: all
Depends: ${perl:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
  libanyevent-serialport-perl, libdevice-onkyo-perl
Description: AnyEvent::Onkyo Perl Module to control Onkyo/Integra AV equipment
 AnyEvent Perl Module that uses the ISCP (serial) and eISCP (TCP) protocol to
 control Onkyo/Integra AV equipment.
 .
 An example script is provide that enables the sending of commands to
 power on/off, change volume, etc. on a networked or serial device.

